《火紅／葉綠》發售後的第一週，共售出了88萬5039份，並不如《紅寶石／藍寶石》。IGN推測銷售量較低的原因在於該遊戲為重製版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/488/488976p1.html|title=Pokemania|publisher=IGN|author=IGN Staff|date=2004-02-02|accessdate=2009-09-15|archive-date=2011-08-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/611N8GJ3l?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/488/488976p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在8月上旬，當《火紅／葉綠》在美國上市的消息發布後，便收到了超過15萬份的預購，是《紅寶石／藍寶石》預購數量的兩倍。任天堂行銷部門的副執行長George Harrison表示：「這個預售數量表示玩家對此的興趣是兩倍以上！」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/540/540749p1.html|title=Pokemon Games Receive Huge Pre-Order Numbers|publisher=IGN|first=James B.|last=Pringle|date=2004-08-20|accessdate=2009-09-15|archive-date=2011-08-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/611N9GXWj?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/540/540749p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲正式上市後，在不到一個月內賣出超過100萬份<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/554/554381p1.html|title=GBA Game of the Month: September 2004|publisher=IGN|first=Craig|last=Harris|authorlink=Craig Harris (journalist)|date=2004-10-05|accessdate=2009-09-15|archive-date=2011-08-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/611NA7o9K?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/554/554381p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2008年3月31日，在全世界的銷售量達1182萬份<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2008/080425e.pdf#page=6|title=Financial Results Briefing for Fiscal Year Ended March 2008|publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date=2008-04-25|page=6|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-04-25|archive-date=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519050029/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2008/080425e.pdf#page=6|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一段時間之後，遊戲的廉價版在{{link-en|任天堂精選|Nintendo Selects}}上販售。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/721/721379p1.html|title=IGN: Player's Choice, Round Two|publisher=IGN|first=Craig|last=Harris|date=2006-07-26|accessdate=2009-06-23|archive-date=2012-05-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67qcL7ekk?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/721/721379p1.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

關於《火紅／葉綠》的評價多數是正面的，遊戲在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上取得81%的總分<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/pokemonfirered?q=Pokemon |title=Pokemon FireRed (gba: 2004): Reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080618002929/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/pokemonfirered?q=Pokemon |archivedate=2008-06-18 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-06-23 }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的Craig Harris 給出9/10的「優秀」評價，讚揚遊戲設計者創作了一個「很適合手持遊戲機的作品」，儘管比不上《紅寶石／藍寶石》，但還是令人滿意。不過 Harris對遊戲畫面不甚滿意，他認為那是「受限的」和「基本的」<ref name="IGN">{{cite web|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/544/544549p1.html|title=Pokemon FireRed Version Review|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|first=Craig|last=Harris|date=2004-09-03|accessdate=2008-12-24|archive-date=2011-08-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/611N2PKmA?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/544/544549p1.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的Greg Kasavin給出8.4/10分，並表示：「《火紅／葉綠》是個傑出的遊戲，充滿比《紅寶石／藍寶石》更多的挑戰，並提供了大量令人欲罷不能的遊戲內容，所有年齡層的玩家都能享樂。」與Harris不同的是，Kasavin讚揚了遊戲的美術，包括多彩的外觀和角色設計<ref name="gamespotreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/pokemonred/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;review|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5xiyMPfm1?url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/pokemonred/review.html?om_act=convert|archivedate=2011-04-05|title=Pokemon FireRed Version Review|last=Kasavin|first=Greg|date=September 7, 2004|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2009-06-23|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》給出8/10的評價，並認為該作品「很有趣」，但認為畫面「與其它手持遊戲相比毫不凸出」。<ref name="GI review"/>

[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]評論家Phil Theobald在滿分五顆星中給了四顆星的評價，表示：「遊戲機制就像剛出來時那樣簡單：探索、捕捉、訓練並建立一個完美的隊伍。但光是這樣就足以吸引你進入遊戲內的世界。」他將《火紅／葉綠》和原本的《紅／藍》畫面互相比較，並讚賞了美術圖形，還讚揚了新功能，例如載入記錄檔時能觀看前次遊玩的畫面，以及多人遊戲功能等。<ref name="gamespy">{{cite web|url=http://gba.gamespy.com/gameboy-advance/pokemon-fire-red/545280p1.html|title=GameSpy: Pokémon FireRed|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|first=Phil|last=Theobald|date=2004-09-07|accessdate=2009-06-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091110142530/http://gba.gamespy.com/gameboy-advance/pokemon-fire-red/545280p1.html|archivedate=2009-11-10}}</ref>

